section.t:
A set of nodes, where each node has both a type, and attributes, where the type 
            can be 
            (1) host: such as src/dst, with attributes such as IP address; 
            (2) AS: which is a group of nodes, i.e., subgraph, with attributes including ASN; 
            (3) router, with subtypes such as BGP-router, with attributes such as IP address.
